---
const trustPills = [
  "Windows first",
  "Local-first harness",
  "Task-centric",
  "Low interruption",
];

const nearbySignals = ["selected text", "dragged files", "current errors", "hover input", "voice hold"];
---

<section class="section-frame relative px-4 pb-18 pt-10 lg:px-0 lg:pb-28 lg:pt-18">
  <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(22rem,0.9fr)]">
    <div>
      <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {trustPills.map((pill) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/7 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.24em] text-cc-cyan uppercase">
            {pill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.28em] text-cc-peach uppercase">Desktop collaboration Agent</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl font-display text-5xl leading-none font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        A tiny desktop Agent that stays near your work instead of pulling you into a chat tab.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/72 sm:text-xl">
        CialloClaw lives at the edge of your desktop with a floating ball entry point. It picks up the task from your current page,
        file, document, error, or note, confirms intent, moves the task through the Agent loop, and delivers the result through
        <code class="rounded bg-white/8 px-2 py-1 text-sm text-white">delivery_result</code>,
        <code class="rounded bg-white/8 px-2 py-1 text-sm text-white">artifact</code>, and
        <code class="rounded bg-white/8 px-2 py-1 text-sm text-white">citation</code>.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a class="focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:scale-[1.02]" href="#download">
          Download for Windows
        </a>
        <a class="focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/6 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10" href="/docs">
          Read docs
        </a>
        <a class="focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/6 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10" href="https://github.com/1024XEngineer/CialloClaw">
          View GitHub
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm text-white/56">
        <span>Nearby signals:</span>
        {nearbySignals.map((signal) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-white/8 bg-slate-950/45 px-3 py-1.5 text-white/76">{signal}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="glass-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-6 lg:p-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-40 bg-linear-to-b from-cc-cyan/10 via-cc-violet/10 to-transparent"></div>

        <div class="relative flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.28em] text-cc-cyan uppercase">Live nearby</p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-white">From floating ball to formal delivery</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/16 bg-slate-950/60 shadow-cc-glow">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-cc-cyan via-white to-cc-violet"></div>
            <div class="absolute h-20 w-20 rounded-full border border-cc-cyan/30"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/8 bg-white/6 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-cc-peach uppercase">Capture</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-white/72">Start from selected text, files, current errors, hover input, or voice without rebuilding context from scratch.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/8 bg-white/6 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-cc-violet uppercase">Govern</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-white/72">Risky actions surface approval_request, authorization_record, audit_record, and recovery_point checkpoints.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/8 bg-white/6 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-cc-mint uppercase">Deliver</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-white/72">Long outputs do not disappear into a bubble. They return as artifacts you can open, inspect, and reuse.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/58 p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.22em] text-white/56 uppercase">Task flow</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base font-medium text-white">input → task → run/step/event → delivery_result</p>
              </div>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-400/16 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-100">low interruption</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
